<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quotation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: white;
            color: #111827;
            /* A4 dimensions typical constraints */
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* ----- HEADER ----- */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .company-slogan {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 400;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        /* ----- METADATA GRIDS ----- */
        .meta-top-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .meta-row {
            display: flex;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .meta-label {
            width: 130px;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .meta-value {
            color: #111827;
        }

        /* ----- CLIENT DETAILS ----- */
        .client-block {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .client-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .client-address {
            color: #374151;
            white-space: pre-line;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* ----- THICK SEPARATOR ----- */
        .separator-thick {
            width: 100%;
            height: 12px;
            background-color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* ----- PROJECT DESCRIPTION ----- */
        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .project-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .project-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ----- ITEMS TABLE ----- */
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .items-table thead th {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        }

        .items-table thead th:nth-child(n+2) {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .items-table thead th:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .items-table tbody td {
            padding: 16px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        /* Inner item rows spacing */
        .items-table tbody tr:not(:last-child) td {
            padding-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .items-table tbody td:nth-child(n+2) {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .items-table tbody td:last-child {
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* A final line below the items */
        .table-bottom-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        /* ----- TOTALS SECTION ----- */
        .totals-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .totals-table {
            width: 320px;
        }

        .total-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #111827;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .total-row.grand {
            background-color: #000;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* ----- TERMS COMPONENT ----- */
        .terms-block {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-left: 4px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .terms-title {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .terms-list {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #374151;
            padding-left: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        /* ----- FOOTER ----- */
        .footer-line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #374151;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .footer-text strong {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-style: normal;
            color: #000;
        }

        .signature-block {
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .signature-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            padding-top: 4px;
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: 280px;
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #374151;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <div>
            <div class="company-name">{{company_name}}</div>
            {{#if company_slogan}}<div class="company-slogan">{{company_slogan}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>
        <div class="doc-title">QUOTATION</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Top Metadata -->
    <div class="meta-top-grid">
        <div>
            <div class="meta-row">
                <div class="meta-label">Quotation No:</div>
                <div class="meta-value">#{{quotation_number}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-row">
                <div class="meta-label">Customer ID:</div>
                <div class="meta-value">{{customer_id}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="meta-row">
                <div class="meta-label">Date:</div>
                <div class="meta-value">{{quotation_date}}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-row">
                <div class="meta-label">Valid Until:</div>
                <div class="meta-value">{{valid_until}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Client Details -->
    <div class="client-block">
        <div class="client-name">{{client_name}}</div>
        <div class="client-address">{{{client_address}}}</div>
        {{#if client_phone}}<div class="client_address">{{client_phone}}</div>{{/if}}
    </div>

    <!-- Thick Separator -->
    <div class="separator-thick"></div>

    <!-- Project Description -->
    <div class="project-grid">
        <div class="project-label">Project Description</div>
        <div class="project-desc">{{project_description}}</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Items Table -->
    <table class="items-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Description</th>
                <th>Qty</th>
                <th>Price</th>
                <th>Total</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each items}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{this.description}}</td>
                <td>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                <td>{{{../currency_symbol}}}{{this.rate}}</td>
                <td>{{{../currency_symbol}}}{{this.amount}}</td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
    
    <div class="table-bottom-line"></div>

    <!-- Totals -->
    <div class="totals-wrapper">
        <div class="totals-table">
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Subtotal</span>
                <span>{{{currency_symbol}}}{{subtotal}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Value-Added Tax</span>
                <span>{{{currency_symbol}}}{{#if tax_amount}}{{tax_amount}}{{else}}0{{/if}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row">
                <span>Others</span>
                <span>{{{currency_symbol}}}{{#if others_fee}}{{others_fee}}{{else}}0{{/if}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="total-row grand">
                <span>Total</span>
                <span>{{{currency_symbol}}}{{total_amount}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Terms & Conditions -->
    <div class="terms-block">
        <div class="terms-title">Commercial Terms & Conditions</div>
        <ul class="terms-list">
            <li><strong>Bank Details:</strong> {{bank_name}} | A/C: {{bank_account_number}} | IFSC: {{bank_ifsc}}</li>
            <li><strong>Validity:</strong> This quotation is valid for a period of {{#if validity_days}}{{validity_days}}{{else}}30{{/if}} days from the date of issuance.</li>
            <li><strong>Execution & Delivery:</strong> {{#if delivery_terms}}{{delivery_terms}}{{else}}Project timelines and milestones will be strictly adhered to as mutually agreed upon prior to commencement.{{/if}}</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Schedule:</strong> {{#if payment_terms}}{{payment_terms}}{{else}}Standard payment terms are 50% advance upon project initiation, with the remaining balance due strictly upon successful completion and handover.{{/if}}</li>
            <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> The pricing structure and strategic information contained herein are classified as strictly confidential and proprietary to {{company_name}}.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer thick line -->
    <div class="footer-line"></div>

    <!-- Footer Content -->
    <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-text">
            Should you require further clarification or wish to proceed with this engagement, please contact your designated representative, <strong>{{contactPersonName}}</strong>, at {{contactEmail}}.<br><br>
            <strong>We sincerely appreciate the opportunity to collaborate with you!</strong>
        </div>
        
        <div class="signature-block">
            <div class="signature-text">
                <strong>Authorization & Acceptance:</strong><br>
                By signing below, I acknowledge acceptance of this<br>quotation and its accompanying terms.
            </div>
            <div class="signature-line">
                Authorized Signature, Name, and Date
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>